{noformat}
Error rendering macro 'gadget' : The gadget at https://domain-name.atlassian.net/rest/gadgets/1.0/g/com.atlassian.jira.gadgets:filter-results-gadget/gadgets/filter-results-gadget.xml was not added to this Confluence instance yet.
